item.title: Any1 know how to enable this startup thing when a new player joins 667/728 rsps
item.dc:creator: @wrrion15 wrrion15
item.description:
@wrrion15 wrote:

Go to settings.java and find this public static final String START_CONTROLER
Change it to: public static final String START_CONTROLER = "HomeCutScene";
